acceptOwnership().details: The new owner accepts the ownership transfer.

buy(uint256,uint256,address).details: Buy numa from token (token approval needed)

extractRewards().details: transfers rewards to rwd_address and updates reference price

getBuyNuma(uint256).details: Estimate number of Numas from an amount of token

getBuyNumaSimulateExtract(uint256).details: Estimate number of Numas from an amount of token with extraction simulation

getSellNuma(uint256).details: Estimate number of tokens from an amount of numa

getSellNumaSimulateExtract(uint256).details: Estimate number of tokens from an amount of numa with extraction simulation

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

pause().details: pause buying and selling from vault

paused().details: Returns true if the contract is paused, and false otherwise.

pendingOwner().details: Returns the address of the pending owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

rewardsValue().details: returns the estimated rewards value of lst token

sell(uint256,uint256,address).details: Sell numa (burn) to token (numa approval needed)

setBuyFee(uint16).details: Set Buy fee percentage (exemple: 5% fee --> fee = 950)

setOracle(address).details: set the IVaultOracle address (used to compute token price in Eth)

setSellFee(uint16).details: Set Sell fee percentage (exemple: 5% fee --> fee = 950)

setVaultManager(address).details: set the IVaultManager address (used to total Eth balance of all vaults)

transferOwnership(address).details: Starts the ownership transfer of the contract to a new account. Replaces the pending transfer if there is one. Can only be called by the current owner.

unpause().details: unpause buying and selling from vault
